    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnationis
                        eius millesimo centesimo trigesimo octavo, decimo kalendas madii, indictione
                        prima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name ref="Cuneradus"
                            >Conradus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Morectus"
                                >Morectus</name></persName>, germani filiorum quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName>, et
                                <persName><name ref="Bona">Buona</name></persName> relicta quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Ghermundus">Iermundi</name></persName> et filia
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Gicus">Gichi</name></persName>, quia
                        consentiente mihi qui supra Buona suprascripti germani, in cuius mundium ego
                        visa sum esse, comuniter nos (…) pro remedio anime Iermundi germano nostro
                        et viro qui quondam fuit meo (…) offerimus tibi deo et <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3209" key="#Bridges/pontoons #Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Bridges/pontoons">ponti</rs> et <rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >ospitali</rs> de Arno</orgName> quod est fundatum in loco qui
                        vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3200">Ficechio</placeName> videlicet
                        integris tribus petiis de terris nostris illis quibus. Una ex ipsis est
                        posita in loco qui vocatur <placeName key="#Roads" ref="#places/3210">Putho
                            Ursi</placeName>, que tenet unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>, aliut caput cum ambobus lateribus tenet in terra nostra
                        qui supra germani. Alia petia posita in eodem loco, tenet unum caput cum uno
                        latere in terra nostra qui supra germani, aliut caput tenet in terra de
                        filiis <persName><name ref="Musciante">Muscianti</name></persName>, aliut
                        latus tenet in terra de filiis <persName><name ref="Ildebrandinus"
                                >Ildebrandini</name></persName>. Tertia petia cum <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs> super se habente est posita in loco qui vocatur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3209" key="#Wine">Cafagio</placeName>, tenet unum caput in
                        terra <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1704">Sancti Petri</orgName>, aliut
                        caput tenet in terra de filii <persName><name ref="Belloctus"
                                >Bellocti</name></persName>, latus unum tenet in terra de
                                <persName><name ref="Libornacus">Libornachi</name></persName>, aliut
                        latus tenet in terra de suprascriptis filiis Ildebrandini. (…) <ref>Pena in
                            duplum. Maledizione.</ref> Quia in tali hordine hanc cartulam <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Hubertus">Ubertum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> scribere rogavimus. Actum in loco qui
                        vocatur Ficechio, in capite suprascripti ponti. Singna manuum suprascripti
                        germani Buone, qui comuniter et consentienter hanc cartulam fieri
                        rogaverunt. Singna manuum <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Malagalgia"
                                >Malagalgie</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Frankus">Franchi</name></persName> germani filiorum quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrandi</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Pampanus">Pampanii</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Morectus">Morecti</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugo">Ugoni</name></persName> filii
                        quondam Gichi et aliorum plurimum rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>.
                        (L) Ubertus donni inperatoris notarium post tradita complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
